quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,1,"Ya'. Sin.",footnotes:180624:1
  36,2,"By the Wise Qur'an,"
  36,3,"you are truly among the Messengers,",footnotes:180625:1
  36,4,"on a Straight Way,"
  36,5,"(and this Qur'an) is a revelation from the Most Mighty, the Most Compassionate",footnotes:180626:1
  36,6,"so that you may warn a people whose ancestors were not warned before wherefore they are heedless.",footnotes:180627:1
  36,7,"Surely most of them merit the decree of chastisement; so they do not believe.",footnotes:180628:1
  36,8,"We have put fetters around their necks which reach up to their chins so that they are standing with their heads upright,",footnotes:180629:1
  36,9,"and We have put a barrier before them and a barrier behind them, and have covered them up, so they are unable to see.",footnotes:180630:1
  36,10,"It is all the same for them whether you warn them or do not warn them for they shall not believe.",footnotes:180631:1